Cell.Text: [S] G|Keep Mother's staff. Think of it as payment. I want to leave everything from this cursed place behind. Goodbye. And thank you.
I didn't want to, but she attacked to try and keep me from leaving. | I just can't be a part of this place any more! The things we do here - evil, evil things. No more!

We were supposed to find a sacrifice. Human sacrifice. I told her I couldn't do it and she attacked. | I've done horrible things living here, but never taken an innocent life. I couldn't just find some person for them to kill.
